```plantuml
@startuml ballerina-platform_asyncapi-tools

package "AsyncAPI Tools" {
    [AsyncApiCmd] as cmd
    [AsyncApiToBallerinaGenerator] as gen
    [BallerinaToAsyncApiGenerator] as reverse
    [SchemaHandler] as schema
    [WebSocketHandler] as ws
    [AuthHandler] as auth
    [ErrorHandler] as error
}

[API Definition Files\n(*.yaml)] as yaml
[Ballerina Code Files\n(*.bal)] as bal
[CLI Interface] as cli

cli --> cmd : invokes
cmd --> gen : generates\nfrom
cmd --> reverse : exports\nto
gen --> schema : processes
gen --> ws : handles
gen --> auth : configures
gen --> error : manages
reverse --> schema : processes
reverse --> ws : handles

yaml --> gen : input
gen --> bal : output
bal --> reverse : input
reverse --> yaml : output

@enduml
```